Patch 8.0.1172
Problem:    When E734 is given option is still set.
Solution:   Assign NULL to "s". (Christian Brabandt)
Files:      src/eval.c, src/testdir/test_assign.vim


*** ../vim-8.0.1171/src/eval.c	2017-09-17 23:02:17.172074424 +0200
--- src/eval.c	2017-10-02 19:24:40.484889352 +0200
***************
*** 1704,1710 ****
--- 1704,1713 ----
  						       &stringval, opt_flags);
  		if ((opt_type == 1 && *op == '.')
  			|| (opt_type == 0 && *op != '.'))
+ 		{
  		    EMSG2(_(e_letwrong), op);
+ 		    s = NULL;  /* don't set the value */
+ 		}
  		else
  		{
  		    if (opt_type == 1)  /* number */
*** ../vim-8.0.1171/src/testdir/test_assign.vim	2017-02-23 15:19:59.409451193 +0100
